arts.ttl: Ronaldo's brace keeps Al Nassr's title hopes alive
arts.sum: Cristiano Ronaldo scored both goals as Al Nassr defeated Damac 2-0 and kept alive their Saudi Pro League title challenge on Friday.

arts.ttl: Preview: Al-Nassr vs. Damac - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Friday's Saudi Pro League clash between Al-Nassr and Damac, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
